text: William Martin Sveinson (July 7, 1946 â€“ December 17, 2020) was a Canadian professional poker player and politician. Sveinson was a Member of the Legislative Assembly (MLA) in Saskatchewan from 1982 to 1986. He was a member of the Saskatchewan Liberal Party. Sveinson was born in Wadena, Saskatchewan. Sveinson died on December 17, 2020 in Edmonton, Alberta at the age of 74.William SVEINSON ==References== Category:1946 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Poker players Category:Sportspeople from Saskatchewan
